Name: Data_Set
Description: The Data_Set class is the container for classes and attributes describing the provenance, size and processing details of data sets used by the machine learning model.

Name: data_set_version_id
Description: The data_set_version_id attribute specifies the data set version number.

Name: data_set_size
Description: The data_set_size attribute provides the number of items in the data set.

Name: Training_Set
Description: The Training_Set class belongs to the Data_Set class family and contains attributes that describe the provenance, size, and processing details for the machine learning model training set.

Name: data_set_version_id
Description: The data_set_version_id attribute specifies the data set version number.

Name: data_set_size
Description: The data_set_size attribute provides the number of items in the data set.

Name: Validation_Set
Description: The Validation_Set class belongs to the Data_Set class family and contains attributes that describe the provenance, size, and processing details for the machine learning model validation set.

Name: data_set_version_id
Description: The data_set_version_id attribute specifies the data set version number.

Name: data_set_size
Description: The data_set_size attribute provides the number of items in the data set.

Name: Test_Set
Description: The Test_Set class belongs to the Data_Set class family and contains attributes describing the provenance, size, and processing details for the machine learning model test set.

Name: data_set_version_id
Description: The data_set_version_id attribute specifies the data set version number.

Name: data_set_size
Description: The data_set_size attribute provides the number of items in the data set.

Name: Test_Performance
Description: The Test_Performance class contains information about a trained model's performance on the test set.

Name: performance_measure
Description: The performance_measure attribute specifies the name of the measure (or metric) used to report performance of the model on the test set.

Name: performance_score
Description: The performance_score attribute reports the numeric score the model achieved using performance_measure on the test set.

Name: Trained_Machine_Learning_Model
Description: The Trained_Machine_Learning_Model class is a container for classes and and attributes describing the various parameters specified to the Machine Learning Algorithm.

Name: trained_model_version_id
Description: The trained_model_version_id attribute specifies the trained model version number.

Name: trained_model_name
Description: The trained_model_name attribute specifies the name of the model used.

Name: Machine_Learning_Algorithm
Description: The Machine_Learning_Algorithm class is a container for classes and and attributes describing the algorithm type and learning style used.

Name: algorithm_learning_style
Description: The algorithm_learning_style attribute describes the type of learning style adopted by the algorithm to model a problem.

Name: Semisupervised_Learning
Description: Both labeled data and a large amount of unlabeled data have been used during training.

Name: Supervised_Learning
Description: Supervised_Learning indicates that labeled data has been used to teach models to yield the desired output.

Name: Unsupervised_Learning
Description: The algorithm has not received any labeled data and has discovered patterns on its own from untagged input.

Name: algorithm_type
Description: The algorithm_type attribute describes the kind of algorithm used, such as a regression model, neural network, tree, etc.

Name: Convolutional_Neural_Network_Classifier
Description: The algorithm used for data analysis is a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) Classifier.

Name: algorithm_name
Description: The algorithm_name attribute specifies the name of the algorithm used.

Name: Machine_Learning
Description: The Machine_Learning class is a container for all machine learning information in the label.
